    "Whereas these factors increase the effectiveness of LLMs across all contribution types, the inherent characteristics of maintenance tasks-well-defined solution spaces-lead to a larger boost in maintenance commits compared to code development, particularly in high-context environments.",
    "To understand how the patterns we've observed might evolve as LLMs improve, we leverage the significant upgrade to GitHub Copilot's underlying model in June 2022.",
    "This upgrade enhanced the model's contextual understanding and code generation capabilities.",
    "7 We introduce an additional difference-in-differences term using a dummy variable for the post-upgrade period (afterCopilotUpgradet), allowing us to estimate how the impact on different innovation-type changes with improved LLM capabilities.",
    "Table 7 presents these results for both language pairs."
